{"tid":2500820,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"為何買Bond ETF都唔買直債","createTime":"2021-04-23T02:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T07:45:27.000Z","uid":264908,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3c10aab80aa70efb7542d95ae7f2f09a4ad5a358","tid":2500820,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"點解有啲Po成日叫人買Bond ETF或債基都唔買直債？<br />\n前者收息要扣30%稅，後者收息一個仙都唔使俾&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2b157f64bd931bf790bb8aedecf7622c0de1c9","tid":2500820,"uid":143540,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"兩樣都無買，純9估：<br />\n1. 入場資本門檻較高<br />\n2. 要自己研究個債<br />\n3. 債ETF個價會升但直債唔會"},{"pid":"a4a3772018372dd7a331005050d4d4eb5dee31dc","tid":2500820,"uid":54884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"因為唔夠20萬美金"},{"pid":"0376d720cd4b4bb335eb69e6267ac9616701d46c","tid":2500820,"uid":288803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"何不食肉糜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec13da7710f49fb35993efdbbabee3ee173de80","tid":2500820,"uid":22243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"你買直債 一執笠就gg<br />\n<br />\nBond ETF 有一大堆債 執一間都無問題"},{"pid":"c6068f7476ee64f7e7a03cd9cc617152ffcf0a40","tid":2500820,"uid":175112,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"平衡風險 同有人鍾意股票 有人鍾意基金 etf 一樣 <br />\n利申 鳩up"},{"pid":"00dfc8ab2357c9c7dfeacc0d38e3a9517e2e1b1f","tid":2500820,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"Bond ETF 幫你買賣 rebalance <br />\n例如買10年期ETF，會賣走2030年到期債券，買入2031年債券<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩估"},{"pid":"fb941e185a003d5ca42533468a81624eccded35d","tid":2500820,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"前者收息要扣30%稅&lt;&lt;老美先係姐。你可以買其他market<br />\nBond etf分散風險。直債要時間揀同集中風險高。但砌得靚既如果唔default可保本唔會賺息蝕價。各有各好"},{"pid":"a8127e9752f9c610620ba40550978704988d1481","tid":2500820,"uid":306621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"2樣都有買<br />\n直債要研究<br />\nETF 回報比較低, 但比較簡單<br />\n<br />\n純BOND ETF 應該唔洗收TAX"},{"pid":"8a9b380f2d5d3e372bc6439ce0daf3a407cb9b1c","tid":2500820,"uid":264908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8127e9752f9c610620ba40550978704988d1481","tid":2500820,"uid":306621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"2樣都有買<br />\n直債要研究<br />\nETF 回報比較低, 但比較簡單<br />\n<br />\n純BOND ETF 應該唔洗收TAX"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"純bond ETF唔使收稅-＞按持美債比例計？<br />\nRebalance 債券Portfolio -&gt;如果自己用screen sort到一堆投資級別年利率4到5厘左右債劵，咁咪仲簡單唔使硬食30%稅（美企或市政債）<br />\n非美債ETF或fund唔使食30%稅，以穩陣而實際年利率過4厘計，除美企或市政債，就只能考慮歐洲、日企、個別澳、加、韓、台企直債，但裏面搵到近4厘直債非常少，仲要先蝕匯價，美直債幾乎唔使蝕匯價。<br />\n近排見加密貨幣同股票風高浪急，又coin苦主圍爐區gme strong hold乜春社工輔導區，搞咁春多嘢食晒驚風散，不如買穩穩陣陣直債好過搞咁多花臣啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}